{"tid":1943362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最後6日】係咪要光復立會 選特首？","createTime":"2020-03-25T15:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T15:49:05.000Z","uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f51932185ca015f429da858b7de5bfedf73af74e","tid":1943362,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更改功能組別/選民資料(4月2日截止)</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gccop.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgccop.htm&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=a5ee07f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gccop.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/fcindelector.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Ffcindelector.htm&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=cdc245b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/fcindelector.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n/<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>只要搶到其中一個界別就足以令中共唔夠票欽點特首</strong></span><strong>。而關鍵的截止日期是2020年4月2日！</strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即係唔夠1星期！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咪住，特首選委的登記截止日期不2021年4月2日嗎？為何提早了12個月？無錯，但這是表面日期，實情有不少界別<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>需要你在登記前12個月已加入或成立了某些協會或團體，才可以符合資格登記</strong></span>。換言之，若果<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">錯過了2020年4月2日的限期，差不多等同白白放棄特首選委這條戰線！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/變天最關鍵的特首選委界別-唔夠四個月就靜靜輸了/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5-%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E8%BC%B8%E4%BA%86%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=e1df0fd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5-%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E8%BC%B8%E4%BA%86%2F&h=33045616\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/變天最關鍵的特首選委界別-唔夠四個月就靜靜輸了/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>換特首只需四萬素人新血</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/換特首只需四萬素人新血-三個月截止/?fbclid=IwAR34sM83ckPOfBg_4RckJqjhlc6uArLn_gK2vBGnlskYkOVyR-XF6InDHXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%8F%9B%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E5%9B%9B%E8%90%AC%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%80-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR34sM83ckPOfBg_4RckJqjhlc6uArLn_gK2vBGnlskYkOVyR-XF6InDHXc&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=0897d4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%8F%9B%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E5%9B%9B%E8%90%AC%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%80-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR34sM83ckPOfBg_4RckJqjhlc6uArLn_gK2vBGnlskYkOVyR-XF6InDHXc&h=d96e9d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/換特首只需四萬素人新血-三個月截止/?fbclid=IwAR34sM83ckPOfBg_4RckJqjhlc6uArLn_gK2vBGnlskYkOVyR-XF6InDHXc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【功